(31, 'movie', 'adventure;animation;comedy', 'The Book of Life', '', 'the-book-of-life-2014', '3684cd3af57141b5ec3ae8e49837ca97a32f470a.jpg', 2014, 0000, 'Manolo, a young man who is torn between fulfilling the expectations of his family and following his heart, embarks on an adventure that spans three fantastic worlds where he must face his greatest fears.', 'This film is a vibrant fantasy-adventure, tells the legend of Manolo, a conflicted hero and dreamer who sets off on an epic quest through magical, mythical and wondrous worlds in order to rescue his one true love and defend his village.', 'Гэр бүлийнхээ итгэлийг хүлээх, зүрх сэтгэлээ дагах хоёр замын дунд гацсан хөөрхий залуу Маноло гурван өөр ертөнцөөр аялах боломжтой болно. Гэвч энэ ертөнцөд тэрээр хамгийн том айдсаа давж гарах ёстой. ', 'Маноло ид шид, үлгэр домог, гайхамшиг тохиолдох гурван өөр ертөнцөөр аялаж, жинхэнэ хайр, төрж өссөн тосгоноо аврахын төлөө тэмцэнэ. ', '<iframe width="560" height="315" src="//www.youtube.com/embed/lOidYzmVrgk" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen></iframe>', '<span class="imdbRatingPlugin" data-user="ur37598576" data-title="tt2262227" data-style="t1">\r\n<a href="http://www.imdb.com/title/tt2262227/?ref_=tt_plg_rt"\r\n><img alt="The Book of Life (2014) on IMDb" src="http://g-ecx.images-amazon.com/images/G/01/imdb/plugins/rating/images/imdb_46x22.png">\r\n</a></span>\r\n<script>\r\n(function(d,s,id){var js,stags=d.getElementsByTagName(s)[0];\r\nif(d.getElementById(id)){return;}js=d.createElement(s);js.id=id;\r\njs.src="http://g-ec2.images-amazon.com/images/G/01/imdb/plugins/rating/js/rating.min.js";\r\nstags.parentNode.insertBefore(js,stags);})(document,''script'',''imdb-rating-api'');    \r\n</script>                    ', 95, 13, '20th Century Fox', 'Jorge R. Gutierrez', 'Jorge R. Gutierrez (screenplay), Douglas Langdale', 0, 0, 'https://www.facebook.com/bookoflifemovie', 'http://www.bookoflifemovie.com/', '2014-10-17', 'Diego Luna, Zoe Saldana, Channing Tatum', '', 0, 0, 0, 1,