(115, 'series', 'comedy;drama', 'Jane by Design', '', 'jane-by-design-2011', '4348b3f6b188312ea04921c06844170660dd2c59.jpg', 2011, 0000, 'A case of mistaken identity has a dateless high school outsider living a double life as a twenty-something career girl in the fashion world.', 'In the introductory season of "Jane by Design", Jane Quimby (Erica Dasher) is a teenager that leads a double life as a high-school student and an assistant to a fashion executive (played by Andie MacDowell .). The comedy-drama picks up on Jane''s struggle to balance both worlds while taking on life''s dramas and maturing. Special appearances from Patricia Field, Stefano Tonchi, and Betsey Johnson among many others from both fashion and design acclaim.', 'Жэйн хоёр төрлийн амьдралтай. Нэг нь 10 жилийн сургуулийн сурагч, нөгөө нь загварын ертөнцийн алдарт дезайнерийн хорин хэдэн настай туслах.', 'Жэйн Квимби 10 жилийн сургуулийн сурагч. Гэвч сургуулиас гадуур дезайнерийн туслахаар ажилладаг. Энэ хоёр амьдралынхаа тэнцвэрийг олох тун ч хэцүү. Учир нь эгд нь насанд хүрсэн хүн, нөгөөд нь өсвөр насны охин байх ёстой.', '<iframe width="560" height="315" src="//www.youtube.com/embed/otQzYp0x4F4" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen></iframe>', '<span class="imdbRatingPlugin" data-user="ur37598576" data-title="tt1743904" data-style="t1">\r\n<a href="http://www.imdb.com/title/tt1743904/?ref_=tt_plg_rt"\r\n><img alt="Jane by Design (2011– ) on IMDb" src="http://g-ecx.images-amazon.com/images/G/01/imdb/plugins/rating/images/imdb_46x22.png">\r\n</a></span>\r\n<script>\r\n(function(d,s,id){var js,stags=d.getElementsByTagName(s)[0];\r\nif(d.getElementById(id)){return;}js=d.createElement(s);js.id=id;\r\njs.src="http://g-ec2.images-amazon.com/images/G/01/imdb/plugins/rating/js/rating.min.js";\r\nstags.parentNode.insertBefore(js,stags);})(document,''script'',''imdb-rating-api'');    \r\n</script>', 44, 6, 'ABC Family Worldwide', 'April Blair', 'April Blair', 1, 18, 'imdb.com', 'imdb.com', '2011-01-01', 'Erica Dasher, Nick Roux, Rowly Dennis', 'http://kickass.so/usearch/Jane%20by%20Design/', 0, 0, 0, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'imdb.com', 0, 0, '2014-11-19 09:33:23', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(116, 'movie', 'biography;drama', 'Milk (I)', 'Милк', 'milk-i-2008', '979bfc723c38cf1cba0f1f144ae9d3cb8d231b9c.jpg', 2008, 0000, 'The story of Harvey Milk, and his struggles as an American gay activist who fought for gay rights and became California''s first openly gay elected official.', 'In 1977, Harvey Milk was elected to the San Francisco Board of Supervisors, becoming the first openly gay man to be voted into public office in America. His victory was not just a victory for gay rights; he forged coalitions across the political spectrum. From senior citizens to union workers, Harvey Milk changed the very nature of what it means to be a fighter for human rights and became, before his untimely death in 1978, a hero for all Americans. During the last eight years of his life, while living in New York City, he turns 40. Looking for more purpose, he and his lover Scott Smith relocate to San Francisco, where they found a small business, Castro Camera, in the heart of a working-class neighborhood. Then, with support from Scott and from new friends like young activist Cleve Jones, Milk plunges headfirst into the choppy waters of politics. Bolstering his public profile with humor, Milk''s actions speak even louder than his gift-of-gab words. When Milk is elected supervisor for the newly zoned District 5, he tries to coordinate his efforts with those of another newly elected supervisor, Dan White. But as White and Milk''s political agendas increasingly diverge, their personal destinies tragically converge.', 'Ижил хүйстнүүдийн эрхийг хамгаалах тэмцэгч, Калифорниа мужийн захиргаанд сонгогдсон анхны ил ижил хүйстэн Харви Милкийн түүх.', '1977 онд Харви Милк Сан Франциско хотын захиргааны удирдах албан тушаалд сонгогджээ. Сонгогдохоосоо өмнө тэрээр олон нийтэд бэлгийн чиг хандлагаа мэдэгдсэн төдийгүй ижил хүйстнүүдийн эрхийг хамгаалах тэмцэх тухайгаа зарлаж байжээ. Тэрээр хүний эрхийн төлөөх тэмцэл ямар утгай болохыг Америкчуудад ойлгуулсан бөгөөд 1978 онд нас барахад нь Америкчууд түүний баатар хэмээн үзэж байлаа.', '<iframe width="420" height="315" src="//www.youtube.com/embed/Zp0uYT0zDbA" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen></iframe>', '<span class="imdbRatingPlugin" data-user="ur37598576" data-title="tt1013753" data-style="t1">\r\n<a href="http://www.imdb.com/title/tt1013753/?ref_=tt_plg_rt"\r\n><img alt="Milk (2008) on IMDb" src="http://g-ecx.images-amazon.com/images/G/01/imdb/plugins/rating/images/imdb_46x22.png">\r\n</a></span>\r\n<script>\r\n(function(d,s,id){var js,stags=d.getElementsByTagName(s)[0];\r\nif(d.getElementById(id)){return;}js=d.createElement(s);js.id=id;\r\njs.src="http://g-ec2.images-amazon.com/images/G/01/imdb/plugins/rating/js/rating.min.js";\r\nstags.parentNode.insertBefore(js,stags);})(document,''script'',''imdb-rating-api'');    \r\n</script>', 128, 13, 'Focus features', 'Gus Van Sant', 'Dustin Lance Black', 0, 0, 'https://www.facebook.com/MilktheMovie', 'http://www.focusfeatures.com/milk', '2009-01-30', 'Sean Penn, Josh Brolin, Emile Hirsch', '', 0, 0, 0, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'imdb.com', 0, 0, '2014-11-20 02:44:55', '0000-00-00 00:00:00');
